---
Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 260
Tags:
  - Combat-Action=Judgement=The Round of Existence
By: Sri Chandrasekhara Bhâratî Swâmigal
---
If we happen to lose a paltry sum of two rupees, it takes us three
days to get over the grief caused by that loss. But we are prepared to
waste the whole of this far more valuable life without seeking
Knowledge. What can possibly compensate or remedy this colossal loss?
